//   t∞: ℂ-HDC ⊑ deterministic · same-seed ⇒ same-vector ∀ hosts
//   t∞: bind = (a·b)ᵢ = aᵢ·bᵢ ← complex-pointwise-multiply
//   t∞: bundle = ∑ vⱼ then-renormalize-amplitudes-to-unit
